":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2569437194","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2569437194","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjU2OTQzNzE5NA==","status":"current","title":"Mobile","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":504478439},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2569437194/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2569437194/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2569437194/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2569437194/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2569437194","tinyui":"/x/CoAmmQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2569437194","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2569437194/Mobile","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2569437194"}},{"id":"2633400441","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2633400441","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjYzMzQwMDQ0MQ==","status":"current","title":"App Infonet Cobranzas","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":167073886},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2633400441/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2633400441/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2633400441/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2633400441/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2633400441","tinyui":"/x/eYD2n","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2633400441","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2633400441/App+Infonet+Cobranzas","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2633400441"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>La idea es reflejar en la App de IC, cuando tenemos nuevos facturadores, provenientes del C4C. Para este caso, se realizar&aacute; un nuevo modelo que se alimentar&aacute; en base a sentencias SQL (no hay que exponer un endpoint).</p><p /><p><strong>Importante:</strong> </p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Los productos del nuevo modelo de facturadores nuevos (el product_id), ya tienen que estar creados en la tabla Products de billing y su brand correspondiente.</p></li><li><p>No se considera un CRUD para la nueva tabla.</p></li></ol><h2>Estimaci&oacute;n y tasking</h2><table data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"3cb5114a-4fdd-4813-b88a-96b5b05ee229\"><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Modulo</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Detalle</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hrs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>billing-service</p></td><td><p>Nuevo modelo (new_billers) que contendr&aacute; los nuevos facturadores. </p><p>Las columnas a considerar son:</p><p>id, product_id, created_at</p></td><td><p>8</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>billing-service</p></td><td><p>endpoint para retornar los facturadores nuevos y el total de los mismos</p></td><td><p>16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>nuevo-backend</p></td><td><p>endpoint para que llame al nuevo endpoint de billing</p></td><td><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>app</p></td><td><p>Crear en la pantalla principal un componente que muestre la cantidad de facturadores nuevos y todos.</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"105\" ac:original-width=\"115\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230619-190846.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>Cuando se presiona &ldquo;Nuevos&rdquo;, ir a la pantalla donde se muestran esos facturadores nuevos</p></td><td><p>16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>app</p></td><td><p>Consultar endpoint para obtener la cantidad de facturadores nuevos y el listado de los mismos</p></td><td><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>app</p></td><td><p>Pantalla donde se listen los facturadores nuevos. Ejemplo:</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"249\" ac:original-width=\"275\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20230619-191153.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>Cuando se presiona un facturador, hacer el curso normal que tenemos al seleccionar un facturador ya existente (para realizar un pago)</p></td><td><p>16</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Cotingencia</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p>12</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Total</strong></p></td><td><p /></td><td><p><strong>92</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2633302089"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":917},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2633302089/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2633302089/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2633302089/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2633302089/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2633302089","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2633302089/Estimaci+n+Nuevos+Facturadores","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2633302089","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2633302089","tinyui":"/x/SQD1n","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}